    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "<div>\n",
       "<style scoped>\n",
       "    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\n",
       "        vertical-align: middle;\n",
       "    }\n",

   ]

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Log Transformation for normal curve for continuous data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 61,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "num_features=['LotFrontage','LotArea','MasVnrArea','BsmtFinSF1',\n",
    " 'BsmtUnfSF',\n",
    " 'TotalBsmtSF',\n",
    " '1stFlrSF',\n",
    " '2ndFlrSF',\n",
    " 'GrLivArea',\n",
    " 'GarageArea',\n",
    " 'WoodDeckSF',\n",
    " 'OpenPorchSF',\n",
    " 'EnclosedPorch',\n",
    " 'ScreenPorch']\n",
    "\n",
    "for feature in num_features:\n",
    "    df3[feature]= np.log1p(df3[feature])"
   ]
  },

    "from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 113,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "params = {'alpha': [0.0001, 0.001, 0.01, 0.05, 0.1]} #Grid Search cv for hyper tuning\n",
    "folds=5\n",
    "lasso=Lasso()\n",
    "model_cv = GridSearchCV(estimator = lasso, \n",
    "                        param_grid = params, \n",
    "                        scoring= 'neg_mean_absolute_error', \n",
    "                        cv = folds)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 198,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",

     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [

    "Ridge"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 124,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.linear_model import Ridge"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 126,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "params = {'alpha': [0.0001, 0.001, 0.01, 0.05, 0.1]} #Grid Search cv for hyper tuning\n",
    "folds=5\n",
    "ridge=Ridge()\n",
    "model_cv1 = GridSearchCV(estimator = ridge, \n",
    "                        param_grid = params, \n",
    "                        scoring= 'neg_mean_absolute_error', \n",
    "                        cv = folds)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 197,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "{'alpha': 0.1}\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "model_cv1.fit(x_train,y_train)\n",
    "print(model_cv1.best_params_) #getting best parameters i.e value of alpha for lasso regression for  regularization"
   ]
  },
